These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: radish, cranberry, spinach
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, police-officer, bartender
1. the person eating radish is in an even position##4
2. the writer is on the left or right of the bartender##3
3. the writer is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
5. the police-officer is the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | spinach | radish | cranberry |
| Job    | police-officer    | bartender | writer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, hiking, baking
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, motorbike, trike
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | hiking | baking | magic-tricks |
| Transport   | trike    | motorbike     | train        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, skydiving, reading
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, house, funk
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of metal##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | reading     | skydiving | puzzles |
| Music-Genre   | house | metal     | funk  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, crime, zombie
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, badminton, soccer
1. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | crime  | documentary  |
| Sport         | rugby  | badminton | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, rock-climbing, fishing
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, mexican, japanese
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the egyptian##2
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4
3. the japanese is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | hiking   | fishing | rock-climbing    |
| Nationality   | mexican | japanese     | egyptian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, chess, reading
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, badminton, snowboarding
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | chess | reading | gardening   |
| Sport   | snowboarding     | baseball    | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, superhero, thriller
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rabbit, snake
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
2. the person watching action movies is between the owner of the snake and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | action | superhero |
| Pet           | rabbit         | guinea-pig         | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: lemon, cabbage, lettuce
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, horse, bird
1. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the horse and the person eating lemon##2
2. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | cabbage | lettuce | lemon |
| Pet    | horse    | goldfish | bird     |

