.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, indie, salsa
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, volleyball, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the fan of folk##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | indie  | folk  |
| Sport         | snowboarding | volleyball | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, water
There 3 different types of food: banana, cherry, orange
1. the person eating banana is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person eating orange is in an even position##4
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | water      | hot-chocolate |
| Food       | cherry | orange | banana   |

