.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, mechanic, paramedic
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, taxi, motorbike
1. the paramedic is on the right of the mechanic##1
2. the person driving the car is the engineer##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the paramedic##1
4. the paramedic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | mechanic | paramedic | engineer |
| Transport   | taxi | motorbike   | car |

