.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different nationalities: british, malaysian, italian
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, bike
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the british is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
4. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | italian | malaysian | british |
| Transport     | motorbike     | helicopter   | bike        |

