.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, malaysian, australian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, rowing, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the australian##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the malaysian##1
3. the australian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Nationality   | australian  | nigerian | malaysian   |
| Sport         | rowing | biathlon   | handball |

