.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, dancing, fishing
3 different pets are kept: bird, hamster, dog
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the owner of the hamster##2
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the hamster is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | dancing | fishing | board-games |
| Pet     | bird    | dog  | hamster   |

