.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, board-games, writing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, electronic, punk
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is the fan of electronic##1
4. the fan of house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | writing | rock-climbing   | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | house | punk      |

