.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, iced-tea
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, mexican, spanish
1. the spanish is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | milk | fanta | iced-tea |
| Nationality   | mexican   | spanish          | russian |

